Package: luajr
Type: Package
Title: Use LuaJIT Scripting with R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nicholas", "Davies", email = "nicholas.davies@lshtm.ac.uk", role = c("cre", "aut", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1740-1412")),
    person("Mike", "Pall", role = "cph", comment = "Author of the embedded LuaJIT compiler"),
    person("Lua.org, PUC-Rio", role = "cph", comment = "Authors of the Lua scripting language"))
Description: 'luajr' provides an interface to Mike Pall's 'LuaJIT'
    (<https://luajit.org>), a just-in-time compiler for the Lua scripting 
    language (<https://www.lua.org>). It allows users to run Lua code from 'R'.
URL: https://github.com/nicholasdavies/luajr
BugReports: https://github.com/nicholasdavies/luajr/issues
